Object.Field: SNP_TRT : LKM File to Object Storage

COMPONENT NAME: LKM SQL to Object Storage COMPONENT VERSION: 1 AUTHOR: Oracle COMPATIBILITY: ODI 12.2.1.4.0 or above
DESCRIPTION This LKM will upload the result of a SQL query to Oracle Object Storage. Transformations are supported on source only.

Specify the name of logical schema defining the location the temporary file will be stored before uploading to Object Storage. This must be a File technology logical schema. The temporary file will be stored on local file system where ODI agent is running.
Output format used for date datatypes.
Output format used for time and timestamp datatypes.
The number of rows (records read) requested by ODI agent on each communication with the data server.
Field separator character used in unloaded file.

OdiSqlUnload "-FILE=$[tempDirectory]$[tempFile]" "-DRIVER=$[srcDriver]" "-URL=$[srcUrl]" "-USER=$[srcUser]" "-PASS=$[srcPass]" "-FILE_FORMAT=$[tgtFormat]"{# IF ($[tgtFieldSep] != '') #} "-FIELD_SEP=$[tgtFieldSep]"{# ENDIF #} "-ROW_SEP=$[tgtRowSep]"{# IF ($[dateFormat] != '') #} "-DATE_FORMAT=$[dateFormat]"{# ENDIF #}{# IF ($[timeFormat] != '') #} "-TIME_FORMAT=$[timeFormat]"{# ENDIF #} "-CHARSET_ENCODING=$[charSet]"{# IF ($[fetchSize] != '') #} "-FETCH_SIZE=$[fetchSize]"{# ENDIF #} $[sqlText]
